{"tid":413962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如改名叫188討論區","createTime":"2017-09-25T23:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T00:23:36.000Z","uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e6150a0c07503217fe07908af42d69ea0a528200","tid":413962,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:45:12.000Z","msg":"以前有個討論區 向深水埗致敬 改名叫左高登<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hk861.com/data/web/20131203/13860763130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk861.com%2Fdata%2Fweb%2F20131203%2F13860763130.jpg&h=cfa5b615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高登電腦中心（英語：Golden Computer Center；中文名稱「高登」音譯自其英文名稱「Golden」。）是香港著名的電腦產品銷售商場，位於九龍深水埗區深水埗福華街146至152號1樓。<br />\n <br />\n依家有個討論區 向灣仔致敬 改名叫做188<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.primeshop.com.hk/photo/330X250-stretch/b16085_1/%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9188%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.primeshop.com.hk%2Fphoto%2F330X250-stretch%2Fb16085_1%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%2596%25B9188%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B4.jpg&h=83d18aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「東方188商場」位於香港灣仔灣仔道188號。 <br />\n閣下可乘地鐵於灣仔站落車，利用「A3 出口」，向左（東面）沿莊士敦道直行至大有商場位置，此處可見斜對面為OK便利店﹑PCCW等店舖，那裡便是灣仔道，接著再沿灣仔道直行，經過英皇集團中心，再直行，過了克街，直行見到7-ELEVEN，便到「東方188商場」，那裡有超過十間售賣正版遊戲之店舖<br />\n<br />\n連仔 用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ebe2d4d282e04f7e5f9ecd16dd6a92bd49e493","tid":413962,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:46:43.000Z","msg":"上開188 嘅巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f12f2b47577851c104f40b988fbb699b5be421","tid":413962,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:47:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">in 188 we trust</span></span>"},{"pid":"408f4c5659b95fa18e711e29e4be7d8fa6c08875","tid":413962,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:48:25.000Z","msg":"灣仔 vs 深水埗<br />\n188 仔 抬頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4d97982dd50ec003a249b1b545987017ea3400","tid":413962,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9a15fecdb2891985a5df60613fd6d43efe17f3","tid":413962,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df5ce4144b142b8d54e8073ba63d35a46a93634","tid":413962,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:50:45.000Z","msg":"連仔 188<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e039e8317348bf36d83b53ddb9c964a9e48dfe","tid":413962,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T23:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9875519f3b8a8caef0844d9490347ab188769d96","tid":413962,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-